---
title: "checkUpkeep (BaseAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_init: require whenNotPaused, whenAssetOutConfigured
    q_init --> q_loop: auctions = s_allowlistedAssets.values()
    q_loop --> q_check_asset: i < auctions.length
    q_loop --> q_check_assetout_valid: i >= auctions.length
    q_check_asset --> q_skip: assetParams.decimals == 0
    q_skip --> q_loop: continue (no params configured)
    q_check_asset --> q_get_price: assetParams.decimals != 0
    q_get_price --> q_set_assetout_valid: asset == s_assetOut
    q_set_assetout_valid --> q_check_live: isAssetOutPriceValid = isPriceValid
    q_get_price --> q_check_live: asset != s_assetOut
    q_check_live --> q_check_ended: auctionStart != 0
    q_check_live --> q_check_eligible: auctionStart == 0 AND isPriceValid
    q_check_live --> q_loop: auctionStart == 0 AND NOT isPriceValid
    q_check_ended --> q_mark_ended: duration elapsed OR balance below minAuctionSize
    q_check_ended --> q_loop: auction still active
    q_mark_ended --> q_loop: endedAuctions[idx++] = asset
    q_check_eligible --> q_check_usd_value: availableBalance = balanceOf(feeAggregator)
    q_check_usd_value --> q_mark_eligible: availableAssetUsdValue >= minAuctionSizeUsd
    q_check_usd_value --> q_loop: below min size
    q_mark_eligible --> q_loop: eligibleAssets[idx++] = (asset, availableBalance)
    q_check_assetout_valid --> q_clear_eligible: NOT isAssetOutPriceValid
    q_clear_eligible --> q_encode: eligibleAssetsIdx = 0
    q_check_assetout_valid --> q_encode: isAssetOutPriceValid
    q_encode --> [*]: return (upkeepNeeded, performData)

    note right of q_check_ended
        INV-001: Auction ends when duration elapsed OR remaining balance below minAuctionSizeUsd
        INV-002: No new auctions started when assetOut price is invalid
        INV-003: Eligible assets must have valid prices and USD value above minAuctionSizeUsd
    end note
